data.description: Located in the beautiful gated community Heritage Oaks. This 3-bed, 2.5-bath includes an upstairs loft and 2-car garage combining modern comfort with an unbeatable location. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating an ideal setting for entertaining. A standout feature is the upstairs loft that can be utilized as an office or additional entertaining space. The seller is highly motivated, and will cover a 1 year home warranty,  offering peace of mind for your new chapter in this St. Petersburg hidden gem!
